metadata.dc:description: We show a study about haematologic profile at 214 pregnant women, who came to prenatal control at Gynecology and Obstetrics service in the Hospital General de México. This study was realized to stablish the haematologic profile and to have better basis for interpret the different changes that ocur during pregnancy.
metadata.dc:title: Perfil hematológico durante el embarazo.
[Hematologic profile in pregnancy].
